<div class="page-intro prose">
  <h1>Privacy</h1>
  <p class="lede">Short version: no cookies, no personal data, no cross-site tracking.</p>
</div>

<div class="prose">
  <h2>Analytics</h2>
  <p>This site uses <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/web-analytics/" rel="noopener">Cloudflare Web Analytics</a>, a privacy-friendly, cookieless analytics service. It records aggregate information (such as how many people viewed a page and which site they came from) without using cookies, without storing anything on your device, and without building a profile of you or tracking you across other websites.</p>

  <h2>What we do not do</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>No cookies, so no cookie banner.</li>
    <li>No advertising, and no sharing or selling of data.</li>
    <li>No accounts, logins, or forms that collect personal information.</li>
    <li>No tracking of individuals across this or any other site.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>The data shown on this site</h2>
  <p>The figures here come from official public sources (ONS, OBR, the Debt Management Office, HM Treasury, and the IMF). See the <a href="{{ '/sources/' | url }}">sources page</a> for details. This is an independent educational project, not an official government service.</p>

  <h2>Hosting</h2>
  <p>The site is hosted on Netlify, which may process standard server request logs (such as IP address) to deliver pages and protect against abuse, as is normal for any website.</p>
</div>
